 heavily on step-by-step pictures rather than text. While this is helpful in some ways, it’s often difficult to understand which pieces are highlighted and need to go together. It is also tricky to line up pieces, even though they have predrilled holes so your sofa sits straight after it’s assembled.","If the thought of spending time and energy putting together your IKEA sofa doesn’t appeal to you, the company offers an assembly service for an additional cost. When you opt for this service, the couch is assembled at a store, and you can pick it up or have it delivered to your home set up and ready to go. If you would prefer to order a couch that comes assembled, check out the options from <a href=\"/crate-and-barrel-review\">Crate &amp; Barrel</a>."]},"id":"4cbe98e9-a609-410c-bc54-722a4960d6a2","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"e7bb8f27-20f0-4d27-ad33-ff65c5e08385","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["IKEA is a good option if you want to buy a sofa online on a budget and you don’t have to sacrifice style and comfort. Its couch covers can be bought separately, so you can replace yours when it wears out or switch it out for a new color when you update your living room in the future. The sofas come in pieces that you put together yourself; however, IKEA can assemble yours for you for a small cost."]},"id":"e7d423d2-5230-4908-89b7-3c69701ceecd","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_69440","url":"/ikea-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"nicole-johnston","url":"/author/nicole-johnston","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Nicole Johnston","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"nR6fcTbvfudgncYJbhzqDB","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2017-06-07T13:22:53Z","datePublished":"2017-06-07T13:22:53Z","name":"IKEA","synopsis":"IKEA is a well-known online sofa outlet with retail stores located throughout the world.","review":{"verdict":"IKEA offers cheap, s